    <div class="tutorial-paragraph">
      <ul class="tutorial-list">
        <li>
          Input the Long URL: Users provide the original, lengthy URL they
          want to shorten.
        </li>
        <li>
          Generate Short Link: The service generates a new, shorter URL that
          redirects to the original link when clicked.
        </li>
        <li>
          Share the Short Link: Users can then share this short link through
